            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.2.0</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Auto-show keyboard on mobile clients</strong> — The Host now detects when a text field is focused on your Mac and automatically tells connected mobile clients to show their on-screen keyboard.</li>
                    <li><strong>Audio capture infrastructure</strong> — Foundation for upcoming audio streaming feature.</li>
                    <li><strong>Faster disconnect detection</strong> — Reduced timeout for quicker failover.</li>
                    <li><strong>Better TLS/SSL error messages</strong> — Connection errors now show user-friendly messages.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
